name: Air Canada 777-333ER [C-FITW] INAUGURAL Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Here is the arrival of the inaugural flight operated by Air Canada's Boeing 777-300ER on the Calgary-Frankfurt route. As of today, YYC gets daily 777 service until the end of October 2014. Sorry for any shakiness, it was pretty darn cold... Hope you enjoy, and watch in 1080p for better quality.
